                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/camel-2.15.2/camel-core/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/file/FileOperations.java&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/camel-2.15.2/camel-core/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/file/FileOperations.java&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

